HDInsight - allows you to run popular open-source frameworks and create cluster types such as Apache Spark, Apache Hadoop, Apache Kafka
Cognitive services - a collection of domain-specific pre-trained AI models that can be customized with your data
Machine Learning service - a cloud-based environment, used to develop, train, test, deploy, manage, and track machine learning models
Synapse Analytics - a limitless analytics service that brings together enterprise data warehousing and big data analytics
